						<div class="propDesc">
						<p>Apartments Ruzica are located on the south side of Ciovo in the beautiful Mavarstica bay, just 100 m from the sea and beaches.</p>
<p>This beautiful house consists of 3 separate apartments, which combined have the total capacity of 15 people. Apartments Ruzica I., II. and III. (4+1) have 2 bedrooms, living and dining room, bathroom and large sea view balconies with outdoor furniture. Apartments are air-conditioned, equipped with LCD SAT-TV and WLAN internet.</p>
<p>The outside area is designed as a relaxation area with a small garden with flowers and a shared swimming pool (32 m2). Pool area consists of a  spacious shared terrace with lounge chairs for enjoying hot summer days, outside shower and toilet. Behind the house is a large, spacious shared tavern with an indoor fireplace, large wooden dining table and chairs for 12 people and summer kitchen. Interesting tavern in traditional Dalmatian style is made as a unique place where guests can enjoy Mediterranean dinners. Parking space (garage with place for 1 car per each apartment), buoy (for motor boats) are also on disposal. Children are welcome and high chairs / baby cot are available on request. Smaller pets are allowed on request and charged extra.</p>
<p>Apartment Ruzica I. (4+1) spreads on 60 m2. It is situated on the first floor of the house. Apartment has 2 bedrooms, air-conditioned living/dining room with sofa bed for 1 person, fully equipped kitchen and bathroom. It is suitable accommodation for 5 (4+1) persons.</p>
